{"tid":1118142,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"家用應該要比幾多","createTime":"2019-04-21T07:57:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-26T11:25:32.000Z","uid":226332,"like":9,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":64,"replies":[{"pid":"32dd6e08bd23d3ededda7f9a57a8cadb20291ea6","tid":1118142,"uid":226332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T07:57:12.000Z","msg":"小弟就黎Grad，屋企人都開始問家用嘅事<br />\n<br />\n假設人工14000-15000左右，你地會比幾多屋企<br />\n<br />\n利申屋企人對我都好好，但佢地話家用應該要比一半，我個人覺得好似太多，我就認為交3000－4000左右，佢地就覺得太少，想問下各位巴絲係會比幾多，係咪真係我太吝嗇呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08e1d649049190fa039b70cf90bf5325f15c3f08","tid":1118142,"uid":60635,"like":44,"dislike":4,"score":40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T07:58:01.000Z","msg":"0<br />\n比家用係港燦行為"},{"pid":"c39bc61bf9116196da246965147bed82d5a74c2f","tid":1118142,"uid":231111,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"32dd6e08bd23d3ededda7f9a57a8cadb20291ea6","tid":1118142,"uid":226332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T07:57:12.000Z","msg":"小弟就黎Grad，屋企人都開始問家用嘅事<br />\n<br />\n假設人工14000-15000左右，你地會比幾多屋企<br />\n<br />\n利申屋企人對我都好好，但佢地話家用應該要比一半，我個人覺得好似太多，我就認為交3000－4000左右，佢地就覺得太少，想問下各位巴絲係會比幾多，係咪真係我太吝嗇呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T07:58:34.000Z","msg":"唔係 差唔多<br />\nFg果陣份人工$14000 果時比$3500<br />\n覺得對得人對得自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a14ee4039a95a47625485137a0927150bd647da2","tid":1118142,"uid":246970,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T08:01:05.000Z","msg":"35%"},{"pid":"3ee5a701f8a2d261799dc1e8f7f957ee6017adf6","tid":1118142,"uid":28619,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T08:01:13.000Z","msg":"其實睇番你老豆老母點對你<br />\n如果以前比過ok多零用<br />\n有比錢玩活動<br />\n有買過野比你<br />\n有樓etc...<br />\n咁應該比返1/3<br />\n當然如果佢地係仆街就1000都嫌多"},{"pid":"799d72d59d40b8c0814c1e366b969f2946275808","tid":1118142,"uid":51250,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T08:04:43.000Z","msg":"最多3千"},{"pid":"8924f46590365eca43352782b6caa97f2a45e13e","tid":1118142,"uid":188148,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T08:10:21.000Z","msg":"5000"},{"pid":"01c308cde4b0543926495f81dc5d0935ec24b87a","tid":1118142,"uid":90946,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T08:12:22.000Z","msg":"Fg一出黎比三千四千夠啦<br />\n拎你一半去供樓層樓留返比你就話<br />\n拎一半老豆拎去賭老母拎去打牌咁把撚咩"},{"pid":"3e238ea010dc7a2b93a0a250d6420e2d0e711961","tid":1118142,"uid":64457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"32dd6e08bd23d3ededda7f9a57a8cadb20291ea6","tid":1118142,"uid":226332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T07:57:12.000Z","msg":"小弟就黎Grad，屋企人都開始問家用嘅事<br />\n<br />\n假設人工14000-15000左右，你地會比幾多屋企<br />\n<br />\n利申屋企人對我都好好，但佢地話家用應該要比一半，我個人覺得好似太多，我就認為交3000－4000左右，佢地就覺得太少，想問下各位巴絲係會比幾多，係咪真係我太吝嗇呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T08:15:13.000Z","msg":"問下佢地有冇俾一半人工自己老豆老母先啦"},{"pid":"a912f464635f28db939ac6482ecb7f9a2fb7f8c8","tid":1118142,"uid":133946,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T08:16:43.000Z","msg":"睇屋企情況"},{"pid":"b9c8a40a849ebf89a105cd1c4338ca4aa4a17729","tid":1118142,"uid":60980,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a912f464635f28db939ac6482ecb7f9a2fb7f8c8","tid":1118142,"uid":133946,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T08:16:43.000Z","msg":"睇屋企情況"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T08:20:27.000Z","msg":"冇錯<br />\n我半份糧家用<br />\n<br />\n有同事屋企冇負擔成份糧拎去玩<br />\n冇得比"},{"pid":"95a71b2b0a6f785ea682eba3510e46f860818ae0","tid":1118142,"uid":226332,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"3ee5a701f8a2d261799dc1e8f7f957ee6017adf6","tid":1118142,"uid":28619,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T08:01:13.000Z","msg":"其實睇番你老豆老母點對你<br />\n如果以前比過ok多零用<br />\n有比錢玩活動<br />\n有買過野比你<br />\n有樓etc...<br />\n咁應該比返1/3<br />\n當然如果佢地係仆街就1000都嫌多"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T10:50:34.000Z","msg":"舊時屋企好窮，基本上冇玩具冇娛樂冇興趣班，但生活都幾開心，依加經過佢地嘅努力，環境變好左好多，基本上生活無憂，而且佢地都對我好好，所以都考慮緊會比1／3"},{"pid":"e815af6ce394bfa06fdb3c8f2d47c1d925492a70","tid":1118142,"uid":41821,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T10:51:14.000Z","msg":"人工既4-5成"},{"pid":"070fbbfb94fbeaf2d8cac338a6e933bd5990a6fe","tid":1118142,"uid":226332,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a912f464635f28db939ac6482ecb7f9a2fb7f8c8","tid":1118142,"uid":133946,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T08:16:43.000Z","msg":"睇屋企情況"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T10:51:25.000Z","msg":"屋企生活無憂，未窮到等我家用開飯"},{"pid":"790479453eb1888b6c8b3bfb1fa4bda1e6ced77b","tid":1118142,"uid":57035,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T10:52:34.000Z","msg":"畀一半 有撚病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4466d9f9d89600b505493e410a6d09b816b25b9f","tid":1118142,"uid":226332,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T11:01:36.000Z","msg":"唔知係咪我嘅諗法太自私，我自己係覺得屋企夠用，維持到日常開支就得。我認為佢地要為我未來著想下，做仔嘅終有一日會結婚會搬走，會有自己嘅家庭，如果我開始就已經比我一半人工，扣哂日常開支我都應該幾難有錢剩低，可能最低一個月儲得幾千蚊，咁要幾時先買到樓同結婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我有閒錢嘅又唔會對佢地吝嗇嘅，第時出左黎做野，可以嘅都會請下佢地去玩，食飯咁。同埋我又唔會唔養佢地，佢地話冇錢嘅我點都會比佢地。<br />\n<br />\n同埋家用一開始比得多，你之後話比唔可以比咁多，比得少左佢地會點諗。。。<br />\n<br />\n加家用係唔會有人有意見嫁嘛，但減家用就。。。。。"},{"pid":"b14dcdf798b393cf1a973f9b1f86d99dcd658e85","tid":1118142,"uid":21488,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T11:04:43.000Z","msg":"屌萬4萬5學乜撚野人比家用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5170faacbc3b74ffe5ec7c72f2d0ae494bccd824","tid":1118142,"uid":74848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":